.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, manager, photographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, january
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
House: cape-cod, victorian, farmhouse
 1. the owner of the pony is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the cape-cod house is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the fisherman is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Job          | fisherman    | manager | photographer          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Birthday   | january      | april   | july    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| House         | victorian | cape-cod  | farmhouse |

