 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes light-blue##2
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in october##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
