3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, weightlifting
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, davidoff, fonseca
 1. the townhouse house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person traveling to boston##2
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is between the tower house and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the engineer is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
