 3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the fan of gospel is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person eating lettuce##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Music-Genre         | d&b     | classical     | gospel  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Food   | eggplant  | cherry     | lettuce |
| Color           | pink        | apricot | lavender     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

