.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, pop, rock
3 different games are played: snooker, chess, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, fonseca, vegafina
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
4. the blend-smoker is between the person playing snooker and the fan of pop##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the fan of rock and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person playing chess is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

